The paper deals with consensus algorithms in distributed systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions applications in opinion dynamics and flocking, which are topics related to Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
